 Hayden Separator Antique Shop A Very Merry CHRISTMAS to You All! 2nd Annual Christmas Present Special With each purchase over $50.00-$99.99 (before taxes), you will receive any antique Christmas present you chose from under our Christmas tree that is wrapped in red paper. With each purchase over $100.00 (before taxes), you will receive any antique Christmas present you chose from under our Christmas tree that is wrapped in green paper. Each gift is something I randomly pick from our antique shop to wrap and put under our tree. The gift's value is about 1/4+ of the required purchase amount. I chose treasures that I think people who like rustic antiques might like to have. Also, in addition to our annual Christmas Present Special, I've decided to give out blue or red gift bags for purchases from $5.00 through $49.99 (before taxes). These are not antiques or extravagant gifts but just something to say thank you for your business and may you have a Very Merry Christmas. The Christmas season is our most favorite time of the year. If the word "Christmas" offends anyone, we don't really care! I can't imagine being "offended" by the names of anyone else's holiday. For those of you who are not offended or just don't care, why don't you come visit our festively decorated shop. Window shoppers/browsers are also always welcome -no purchase necessary. Just come and take a look around our 9 room shop and see if we can get you into the Christmas spirit while sipping on complementary hot cider, wassail, coffee, tea or cocoa. Our shop consists of 3 rooms full of primitive/rustic antiques, 1 room with higher end antiques, 2 rooms with more common antiques and 3 rooms stocked with flea market/garage sale type items. We are also selling cranberries at $2.00 per pound. In our Cranberry Room, we recently set up our full antique legendary Hayden sorting line which consist of our blower, elevator, separator and front sorting trays. Watch as our cranberries are sorted the same way as they were over 100 years ago. Our antique shop is located in a former cranberry screen house which was called "The New England Cranberry Sales Company" (built in 1918) where the same process took place over 90 years. Before visiting us, we strongly suggest that you call, text or email us ahead of time to avoid disappointment just in case something comes up and we cannot be here to greet you. Hours: Monday - Friday 12 noon - 6 PM Saturday 10 AM - 4 PM Sunday 12 noon - 4 PM We except all major credit cards and cash of course. But no checks of any type -- sorry. Hayden Separator Antique Shop Hayden Mfg. Co. Inc. 70 Carver Rd. W. Wareham MA We are proudly celebrating 124 years in our family business supplying the cranberry industry with goods and services. This is our 10th year in the antique business. We are an accredited business and have an A+ rating with the Better Business Bureau. **Please note to dress warm as we only have heat in two of our rooms. We are looking forward meeting you and sharing the history of our family business with you. A very merry Christmas and a Happy New Year to all of you!

Super rare original color Chromolithograph Hawaiian fish prints from 1903. Over 50 available of various fish. Please email for a viewing . Prices range from $150-200 each A beautiful original and very scarce color chromolithograph from a very rare 115 year-old book, The Bulletin of the United States Fish Commission, Vol. XXIII for 1903, by George M. Bowers. The Aquatic Resources of the Hawaiian Islands: Part 1 - The Shore Fishes by David Starr Jordan and Barton Warren Evermann. Color illustrations based on oil and water color paintings of living specimens by Charles Hudson, A. H. Baldwin, and Kako Morita. Color lithography by Julius Bien and Co., NY. There were only 250 copies of this report made, making these books very rare and expensive Each plate has the name of the book in top left corner, plate number in top right corner, name of artist in bottom right, name of printer bottom left and right corner, and name of fish under fish. This single-sided plate with no text on the verso, printed on a very interesting heavier paper which measures approximately 10 1/2" wide and 7 1/2" high. The plate shows some yellow toning that is typical of plates this old adding a nice patina. The plate is in great condition. Each plate has the holes at the top of the plate where it was attached in which it came. It is a little rough; however, can easily be matted out and framed.  Hayden Separator Antique Shop A Very Merry CHRISTMAS to You All! 2nd Annual Christmas Present Special With each purchase over $50.00-$99.99 (before taxes), you will receive any antique Christmas present you chose from under our Christmas tree that is wrapped in red paper. With each purchase over $100.00 (before taxes), you will receive any antique Christmas present you chose from under our Christmas tree that is wrapped in green paper. Each gift is something I randomly pick from our antique shop to wrap and put under our tree. The gift's value is about 1/4+ of the required purchase amount. I chose treasures that I think people who like rustic antiques might like to have. Also, in addition to our annual Christmas Present Special, I've decided to give out blue or red gift bags for purchases from $5.00 through $49.99 (before taxes). These are not antiques or extravagant gifts but just something to say thank you for your business and may you have a Very Merry Christmas. The Christmas season is our most favorite time of the year. If the word "Christmas" offends anyone, we don't really care! I can't imagine being "offended" by the names of anyone else's holiday. For those of you who are not offended or just don't care, why don't you come visit our festively decorated shop. Window shoppers/browsers are also always welcome -no purchase necessary. Just come and take a look around our 9 room shop and see if we can get you into the Christmas spirit while sipping on complementary hot cider, wassail, coffee, tea or cocoa. Our shop consists of 3 rooms full of primitive/rustic antiques, 1 room with higher end antiques, 2 rooms with more common antiques and 3 rooms stocked with flea market/garage sale type items. We are also selling cranberries at $2.00 per pound. In our Cranberry Room, we recently set up our full antique legendary Hayden sorting line which consist of our blower, elevator, separator and front sorting trays. Watch as our cranberries are sorted the same way as they were over 100 years ago. Our antique shop is located in a former cranberry screen house which was called "The New England Cranberry Sales Company" (built in 1918) where the same process took place over 90 years. Before visiting us, we strongly suggest that you call, text or email us ahead of time to avoid disappointment just in case something comes up and we cannot be here to greet you. Hours: Monday - Friday 12 noon - 6 PM Saturday 10 AM - 4 PM Sunday 12 noon - 4 PM We except all major credit cards and cash of course. But no checks of any type -- sorry. Hayden Separator Antique Shop Hayden Mfg. Co. Inc. 70 Carver Rd. W. Wareham MA We are proudly celebrating 124 years in our family business supplying the cranberry industry with goods and services. This is our 10th year in the antique business. We are an accredited business and have an A+ rating with the Better Business Bureau. **Please note to dress warm as we only have heat in two of our rooms. We are looking forward meeting you and sharing the history of our family business with you. A very merry Christmas and a Happy New Year to all of you!

Be your own director and tell your story as never before. Reach for the sky and capture professional-quality footage from a new perspective. With a crystal-clear camera, real-time HD video display, and intuitive flight controls, what will you create? 
 
 
Features: 
 
4K Video, 12 Megapixel Photos

Epic Aerial Video 
 
Imagine amazing, immersive footage at your fingertips. Imagine capturing content fit for the big screen, with crisp images, beautiful resolution, and vivid colors. With an integrated, stabilized camera, your Phantom 3 Professional brings your imagination to life. 
 
 
Easy To Fly 
 
Your Phantom 3 Professional fits into your life and makes flying remarkably intuitive and easy. From takeoff to landing, it is completely under your control, responding to your commands while automatically handling the most complex aspects of safe, stable flight. 
 
Powerful Mobile App 
 
Complete power is at your fingertips. Control the camera and change flight settings, all from your mobile device. 
 
Live HD View 
 
Experience a new view of your world, over distances up to 1.2 miles (2km) and in real time. Simply connect your phone or tablet, and a 720p HD view of everything your camera sees as you fly is displayed live. This immersive view streams to you in absolute clarity, enabling you to get that perfect shot and experience flying in a unique way. 
 
This live view is made possible by DJI Lightbridge image transmission technology that is used by professional cinematographers and photographers who demand only the best. Fly while seeing everything in HD, and feel what it's like to be above your world without ever leaving the ground. 
 
 
Intelligent Battery 
 
Higher voltage, more energy, and greater power combine to give you a vastly improved flight experience. This upgraded Intelligent Flight Battery has built-in sensors that let you know the status of your battery in real time, so you always know how long you can continue flying and when it's time to recharge. Recharging is fast and easy, and the Phantom 3 Professional Professional comes with an upgraded charger for substantially reduced charge times. 
 
 
Complete Control 
 
Keep your Phantom 3 Professional fully under your command while accessing the most-used features right on the included remote controller. This crucial piece of your flight experience has been engineered specifically for flying camera platforms, making every flight easy, safe, and intuitive. 
 
Unmatched Propulsion 
 
Each motor has the power and precision needed to give you the best flight experience possible. Brushless motors work with lightning-fast ESCs to make your Phantom 3 Professional fast, agile, and responsive. 
 
 
Vision Positioning 
 
Fly indoors, low to the ground, and in GPS-free areas with Vision Positioning technology. Visual and ultrasonic sensors scan the ground beneath your Phantom 3 Professional for patterns, enabling it to identify its position and move accurately. 
 
Worry-Free Autopilot 
 
Automatic elements of your Phantom 3 Professional's intelligent flight system help you fly and are available at the touch of a button.

title: Bose Quietcomfort 3 Acoustic Noise Cancelling Headphones
description:
For sale are a excellent set of Bose Quietcomfort 3 Acoustic Noise Cancelling Headphones.Product Description: Compact, on-ear Quiet Comfort 3 headphones offer a proven combination of Bose noise reduction, audio performance and comfortable fit. Proprietary Bose technologies deliver quality sound from these award-winning headphones - and make listening a pleasure just about anywhere.  Includes two batteries. Call Blake for more info.  
 
From the Manufacturer 
Bose® QuietComfort® 3 Acoustic Noise Cancelling® Headphones 
Bose QuietComfort 3 Acoustic Noise Cancelling headphones 
High-performing noise reduction headphones for travel, work and home 
Enjoy your music and movies even more, with clear and lifelike sound 
Comfortable and lightweight on-ear fit 
Includes two audio cables, one with mic/remote for iPhone®/iPod® control and hands-free calling 
Rechargeable lithium-ion battery, charger and carrying case also included 
Separate the noise from the music 
Leave the noise behind, and get the most from your music. QuietComfort 3 headphones offer a proven combination of Bose noise reduction and audio performance with a comfortable on-ear fit. These award-winning headphones deliver clear, lifelike sound, making listening a pleasure just about anywhere. 
 
Proven performance 
advanced noise reduction 
Advanced noise reduction and a comfortable fit let you enjoy hours of easy listening. 
QC3 headphones feature Bose Acoustic Noise Cancelling technology to electronically identify, then dramatically reduce, the noise around you. You're left with the music you love--or the simple serenity you desire. Proprietary signal processing and audio reproduction technology also provide lifelike performance across the full range of sound--including deep low tones--from small and lightweight headphones. 
 
Create a comfortable escape 
Think of your noisy office, or the bustling activity in train stations and other public places. At the flip of a switch, that background noise is reduced to a whisper. That's when the high quality sound these headphones provide becomes even more apparent. You'll hear more of your music--without having to turn up your music. And the soft-cushioned, easy-on-the-ears fit lets you listen comfortably for hours. 
 
Take calls. Take control 
QC3 headphones come with a cable customized for select Apple products. A three-button remote and microphone let you take calls on your iPhone and control music functions on other Apple devices. You can also purchase a mobile kit that lets your QC headphones work with other cell phones, too. 
 
Bose QC3 headphones advanced noise reduction 
QC3 headphones make an ideal travel companion, effectively reducing the noise around you to create a more tranquil environment. 
Fine traveling companions 
QC3 headphones come with a rechargeable lithium-ion battery and convenient wall charger. You can expect 25 hours of use from a fully charged battery, with a lifespan of approximately 500 charging cycles. An airline adapter plug and protective carrying case are also included. Earcups fold flat for easy storage in the slim case. 
 
Acoustic Noise Cancelling® headphone technology, a proprietary Bose innovation, electronically identifies and reduces noise while faithfully preserving the audio or tranquility you desire. 
Compact on-ear design with proprietary soft cushions that establish a critical acoustical seal - helping to further reduce noise while providing a comfortable fit. 
TriPort® acoustic headphone structure, another Bose exclusive, features tiny vents in the earcups to enable a tonally-balanced audio performance - including reproduction of deep, low notes - from relatively small and lightweight headphones. 
Active equalization electronically tunes the headphones' frequency response, enabling outstanding audio performance. 
QC3 Inline Microphone 
Inline microphone and remote for select Apple products 
Rechargeable lithium-ion battery provides an average of 25 hours of reliable use per charge. Small wall charger also included. 
Interchangeable audio cables, one for general use, and one just for select Apple products, offer greater convenience than permanently connected Y-cables. 
Inline microphone allows for hands-free iPhone conversation and access to certain voice applications, such as VoiceOver and Voice Control, in other Apple products. 
Inline three-button remote switches between calls and music, and controls volume, track selection and voice applications on select Apple products. 
Fold-flat earcups rotate 90 degrees for easy storage and portability in the included case. 
Slim carrying case helps protect headphones and accessories during travel. 
Product Details

Ear cushion outside dimensions	2.88"H x 2.25"W ( 7.5 cm x 6 cm ) 
Weight with cable	4.8 oz (136.1 g)

title: New Canon Pixma MX340 Wireless Inkjet Office All-In-One (Ink Included)
description:
Printer is brand new. Open box. Ink cartridges included. Picked up in San Jose. $99 
 
 
The Canon PIXMA MX340 Wireless All-In-One Photo Printer produces gorgeous color prints (up to 8.5 x 11") at up to 4800 x 1200 dpi resolution, scans documents or images up to 8.5 x 11.7" at 48-bit color depth, makes color copies in as little as 37 seconds, faxes at approx. 3 sec/page (black) or 1 min/page (color) with a 50-page memory, and offers wireless connectivity--plus, its compact good looks mean it fits in just about anywhere. The Auto Photo Fix II feature automatically corrects exposure to optimize the quality of your pictures, and you can also print laser-quality black text or pages directly off the web. The ChromaLife100+ system enables your photos to last up to 300 years when using genuine Canon ink and paper and stored in an archival-quality photo album. 
 
Speed & Quality 
High Resolution: Superb quality and detail in business documents and photos is achieved by 4800 x 1200 maximum color dpi thanks to Canon Full-photolithography Inkjet Nozzle Engineering (FINE) with a patented print head firing ink droplets as small as 2pl. 
High Performance Ink Cartridges: The two Canon ink cartridges are easy to use and to replace, and contain specially formulated inks for great document and photo quality. One is a black cartridge for laser-quality text and one is a multi-color cartridge for pictures. Both are easy to use and replace. 
 
EasyPhoto-Print EX: Print as many images as you want on photo paper up to 8.5 x 11". You can even print multiple pictures on one page. Plus, with one touch of your mouse, EasyPhoto-Print automatically crops images, corrects red-eye, smoothes facial lines and skin tone and even brightens and sharpens faces. 
 
Ease of Use 
Auto Photo Fix II: This built-in technology automatically categorizes your images into one of five types--Portrait, Scenery, Night Scenery, Snapshot with Scenery, and Snapshot with Night Scenery--then applies optimal image and multi-zone exposure correction. Unexposed areas of the photo will be optimized area by area, and faces that are backlit and under-exposed will automatically be brightened and color corrected to help ensure more accurate skin tones for gorgeous images. 
Fully-Integrated Auto Document Feeder: The built-in 30-sheet Automatic Document Feeder (ADF) makes it easy to copy, scan or fax multiple documents without having to load them one at a time. Its full integration makes it easier to fit into tight spots. 
 
Dual Color Gamut Technology: This built-in technology automatically optimizes your originals so copies stay true to it, time after time. 
 
Auto Scan Mode: Automatically recognizes the type of original, then scans and saves with the appropriate settings when accessed through the printer menu. 
 
QuickStart: Powering up your printer is now faster than ever. After pressing the power button you can begin inputting commands in approximately 2 seconds. 
 
Easy-WebPrint EX: Print as many images as you want on photo paper up to 8.5 x 11". You can even print multiple pictures on one page. Plus, with one touch of your mouse, EasyPhoto-Print automatically crops images, corrects red-eye, smoothes facial lines and skin tone and even brightens and sharpens faces. 
 
Connectivity 
Built-In Wireless: Print or scan wirelessly from any Wi-Fi enabled computer around the house. 
Super G3 Fax: The business fax standard for color and PC facsimiles on plain paper meets the home office workhorse with 20 coded speed dials and up to 50 incoming pages. 
 
iPhone Printing: Print your photos wirelessly from compatible iPhone 3G, 3GS and iPod touch models. 
 
PictBridge & Optional Bluetooth: Thanks to a PictBridge connection you can conveniently print photos directly from your digital camera, DV camcorder or camera phone. Plus, you can print from the optional BU-30 wireless Bluetooth unit. 
 
USB 2.0 Hi-Speed-Plug the cable into your computer for a super-fast connection for your data transfers. 
 
Tap into Great Prints 
Download the FREE Canon Easy-PhotoPrint app. to your iPhone or iPod touch and tap your way to great looking wireless prints with select Canon printers. Visit www.usa.canon.com/iepp for more information. 
Fun Print Projects 
Imagine and explore all the possibilities with Canon's Creative Park website. You'll find lots of fun materials you can download and print for FREE! Enjoy creative crafts such as 3D Paper Crafts, Scrapbooking, Greeting Cards and so much more! 
Canon Generation Green 
Generation Green is Canon's environmental initiative. The MP270 features: 
4 in 1, 2 in 1 Printing--this option allows users to place multiple pages on 1 page, saving up to 75% of your paper supply. 
Reduction in Packaging--the packaging of the iP2702 has been reduced by 36.8% compared to the 2008 model. Downsizing the packaging helps reduces CO2 emissions and waste throughout the whole process of production, from shipping to selling. 
 
ENERGY STAR--25% more efficient than conventional models. By using less energy, these products reduce greenhouse gas emissions and save energy as well as money. 
 
RoHS Compliance--RoHS is a directive from the European Union that restricts the use of hazardous materials found in electronic products. This product restricts the use of cadmium, mercury, lead, hexavalent chromium, Polybrominated Biphenyls (PBB), and Polybrominated Diphenyl Ethers (PBDE). 
 
Hardware Recycling Program--Canon wants to work with our customers to help ensure appropriate recycling of products to help improve the environment and our local communities. 
 
Refurbishing Program--the Canon U.S.A., Inc. refurbishing facility manages all waste stream processes for Canon products, so Canon, not third-party vendors, has full control over recovery and salvage for Canon products. 
 
Inkjet Cartridge Recycling--to contribute to zero landfill waste, Canon is introducing a collection and recycling program for Genuine Canon Inkjet Printer Cartridges. 
 
Energy Star Qualified 
25% more efficient than conventional models. By using less energy, this product reduces greenhouse gas emissions and save energy as well as money.

title: GT RUCKUS 3.0 Three Point Zero flat Blue new parts will trade for
description:
condition: like new 
make / manufacturer: GT 
model name / number: Rukus Three Point Zero 3.0 
asking 969 with two sets of wheels both with disc brakes 
or $635 without Mavic wheels 
 
hey got this nice GT, Three Point Zero, 3.0  
 
will sell or trade, meaning WTS WTF 
 
will trade for Samsung Note 7(after recall), Iphone7 256GB verizon  
PS4, XBOX ONE, NEO GEO new, NEO GEO AES Complete in a box, new or like new, make sure they re new with 8 games for video game trade of equal in price not less, iphone open or recent is the same thing to me as long as its clean without damage. 
 
lots of upgrades and new parts from the bottom up, Mavic AEST hollow out disc brake hubs, Avid AUG2013 BB5, FSA, Bontrager, and WTB,  
 
 
here s the thing the last set of wheels is for this price front is a maxxis look alike rear is intense 2.25 very new also, front 1.95 rear 2.25 disc brakes also avid/hayes same thing, 
 
Here's what I am going to do, 
i will give you options,  
 
"as is" with the wheels set off a Canondale in the last picture everything else will not change, use the above price or 650 
 
want two sets of wheels and discs last picture plus mavic s, add for the Mavic bontrager combo, or 999. 
 
price is firm, meaning 50 bucks off either way is okay, nothing rediculious, addtional parts are add ons meaning add more money. price depends on supply and demand meaning a lot of inquires less likely i will go for less, cash is king, first come first serve, etc... 
 
Get em all, why not, you know you will need both, why wait or have a chance to strip your hubs, keep both. 
 
GT RUCKUS Three Point Zero 6061 aircraft aluminum 
 
I am 5'10, this is slightly bigger, but my friend is 6'2", he feels comfortable, very fast,  
saw him go sideways on a turn, knarly. 
Aside from the stock equipment  
 
Truvativ Hussefelt, i think its right check the spelling, 
all SRAM & Shimano Gears,  
hyper glide x8, this is definitely the drive you want, 2x8 
Truvativ Hussefelt crank,  
Truvativ DH ISIS bottom bearing,  
VP pedals, raised studded, removeable studs. 
Alivio brake and shifter, Acera, etc. 
New tune up and Jagwire cables, orange, matching the orange "3.0" lettering.  
 
 
 
Added, which are very NEW or recent 
 
New tune-up and Jagwire setup, full and complete set, brakes and derailleur,  
orange cables to compliment the bike, it really POPs. 
 
 
the current 2.35 and 2.35 combo came off a Cannondale Jackyle, which lowers the price to 650,  
Mavic can never read the graffiti 727, well its in the picture, if you order these seperate its 600-700 non disc brake setup, already with AEST disc brake hub, new, hollo out hubs with disc brakes Avid BB5, HS1 heat shedding 160 mm calipers, new and way better than what came with the bike, that piece of crap tektro I/O craks under pressure read the forums, i rather use the pull or V tektro than disc. New orange Jagwire that compliments the Orange GT logo, makes the bike pop. 
 
Bontrage Trail B, new, extra lite tires, with Keda inner tubes, the tires can go sideways literally, let the trail shreddin begin! 
 
the bike itself retails for 700-800, depends on where you buy it, plus at least 700-800 in extras, 
everything is half priced, bike and the extras, so if this is not a deal I don't know what is, ah, take it with a grain of salt. 
 
FSA LO SER headset and Suntour shocks dual adjustable shocks w indicator, the label fell out looks like a fox label/ well its both adjustable with a float on the top nob to indicate the level, i await the guru to tell me, well had to change to accomodate the right mounted disc break. 
 
Jagwire Orange, the rest GT, seat post, handle bar, frame with the Aluminum Can Logo all stock, its something flat Blue,very thrasher ish, i guess this targeted young adults or latter teenagers, all in all the best GT i have ridden in a while, stock not so much, at this state with all the upgrades, your' re ready for anything, maybe on the way down, you will see this chic! LOL  
 
WTF will trade for new ultrabook, FGFS, iphone 7+, Pixel Blue New, apple macbook pro, apple macbook air newer the better. 
 
thanks

The TX-NR1009 transforms your living room into an immersive entertainment space. As the world's first receiver to feature DTS Neo:X™, it harnesses 9.2 channels of pristine audio to create expanded soundscapes with spine-tingling ambience. Build quality propels the TX-NR1009 to the very top of the mid-range class. Housed in a rigid, vibration-reducing cabinet are separate power/pre-amp blocks, a massive transformer, and symmetrical L/R channels. This rock-solid base supports high-power amplification and a superb range of connections and processing features. Eight HDMI® inputs handle 3D video from Blu-ray, 4K video upscaled by Qdeo™ technology, and studio-quality lossless audio formats. An Ethernet port lets you incorporate internet radio and networked audio from a PC or media server. And USB ports let you play audio files stored on a flash drive or iPod/iPhone. All your video sources benefit from high-quality HQV® Vida™ technology and independent ISF calibration. And for the dedicated home cinema enthusiast, the TX-NR1009 includes advanced features such as bi-amping, 9.2 multichannel pre-outs, and powered Zone 2 and Zone 3 audio.

title: crafty vaporizer
description:
The new CRAFTY portable Vaporizer by Storz & Bickel is available now! 
The CRAFTY is a portable, battery-powered Pocket-Vaporizer. 
 
The CRAFTY's compact construction with a single Lithium-Ion Battery Power is complemented by a practical one button control: You turn on the CRAFTY with only one keypress. It then heats up automatically until it reaches the default set basic temperature of 356°F (180°C). With a double-click on the button, you activate the booster temperature of 383°F (195°C). When the set vaporization temperature is reached, it is signaled through a short double-vibration and the LED-indicator lamp: The LED changes the color from red to green. 
 
    Full Convection Hot Air 
    Precise electronic control 
    Single Lithium Ion Battery Power 
    High Efficiency Heat Exchanger 
    Super Precise Temperature Control 
    Wireless Bluetooth Multifunction App 
    Automatic switch off 
 
  
 
With the CRAFTY, as well as with the MIGHTY and PLENTY, vaporization functions on the basis of a full hot air convection heating combined with conduction. The convection heating provides an immediate and continuous vaporization, whereas the conduction ensures that there is vapor created from the very first breath. 
 
The Filling Chamber, which is integrated into the Vaporizer, is to be filled with plant material (this is facilitated by the included Filling Aid) and the Cooling Unit with Mouthpiece is to be attached. The Cooling Unit makes sure that the vapor cools down and guarantees optimal flavor and a rich aroma. 
 
The CRAFTY is the smallest STORZ & BICKEL Vaporizer with a size of 4.3 x 2.2 x 1.3 inches (11.0 x 5.7 x 3.3 cm) and a weight of 0.3 lbs (135 g). 
CRAFTY REMOTE CONTROL APP - Individual settings of your CRAFTY through Bluetooth Low Energy 
 
The free CRAFTY Remote Control App offers you the opportunity to set basic and booster temperature of your device according to your personal preferences. Amongst other things, the App allows you to read off the battery charge status on your smartphone, to turn on and off the vibration function of the CRAFTY and to activate an alarm and vibration function for your smartphone. 
 
You can download the CRAFTY Remote Control App for free from the Apple App Store (for iPhone 4s or higher) or from the Google Play Store (for Android 4.3 or higher with blue tooth low energy fully enabled). Simply scan the QR Code with your iPhone and you will be forwarded directly to your App Store.

5. 30 amp electrical service

1. The 24J has been lengthened in line with the rest of the View and Navion lineup, and 25 feet, 8 inches. 
2. This added length now provides for a true 80 inch rear bed that elevates at the headboard for reading and foot of the bed lifts up in the front to access every square inch of storage 
3. This added length also provides for an even larger inline galley

5. This large U shaped dinette now includes ottomans that flip up from each of the forward and rear facing benches, all while conveniently converting into a 45 x 82 inch sleeping surface

title: 2009 Mercedes Benz AMG SL63
description:
I am selling my heavily optioned 2009 Mercedes-Benz SL63 produced by AMG in Affalterbach, Germany. I bought the vehicle in March 2014 with 27,000 miles, it currently has 33,500 miles on the odometer.  
 
This car is in excellent condition -- always garaged and always protected with a car cover when parked outdoors. This is a weekend cruising car perfect for trips down Pacific Coast highway or a top-down jaunt through the city. The V8 engine has immense torque and a low, guttural growl that isn't too aggressive- together with the upgraded suspension package and wider tires makes for exciting highway on-ramps and runs down Skyline Drive.  
 
This SL63 has never been in an accident and does not need any maintenance.  
Standard SL63 options include: 
- Hand-built 6.3L V8 engine producing 518 horsepower/465 lb-ft torque (car came from the factory with a DVD of its engine being built) 
- 7 speed dual clutch manumatic transmission (0.100 sec shifts in manual control mode) with paddle shifters and three driving modes 
-14.2 inch 6-piston ventilated front brakes and 13.0 inch 4-piston ventilated rear brakes 
- AMG Sport Exhaust 
- 19" Wheels with 255/35 front and 285/30 rear Michelin Pilot Sport Pro tires 
- Automatic retracting hardtop that works flawlessly- no binding, hesitation, or issues. No repairs ever needed to this mechanism. 
- 12-way adjustable heated, massaging seats with memory (perfect condition -- no scratches, scuffs, or wear present) 
- Alcantara headliner (in perfect condition) 
- 6-disc stereo-navigation system with 40GB hard drive, Bluetooth connectivity, and voice command. Harmon-Kardon speakers still in perfect condition -- no fading drivers. Sirius satellite radio compatible -- though I never used it.  
- iPhone/mobile audio connection in center console (works with iPhones 4, 5, and 6) -- includes stereo jack for any other portable audio device.  
 
Original MSRP was $159,675, including $21,200 in additive options: 
- Option 219 -- Parktronic: Sensor-assist front and rear collisions detection 
- Option 220 - Distronic: Adaptive Cruise Control  
- Option 033 - Designo interior in Mocha Black (pearlescent medium brown highlights that show up really well in bright sunlight) 
- Option 217 - Red AMG Premium Leather 
- Option H73 - Carbon Fiber trim package (interior and exterior carbon elements) 
- Option 030 - AMG Performance Package including: 19" AMG forged alloy wheels, AMG Limited Slip Differential (LSD), Track-calibrated Active Body Control (ABC) suspension system, AMG performance steering wheel (hollow alloy spokes and flat bottom), increased governing speed to 186mph 
- Suspension lifts to clear obstacles and steep grades in the road 
- Suspension has Comfort (suppresses rough road conditions) and Sport (aggressively enhances handling capability) driving modes which are really significant, unlike many German sports cars where these modes only make minor changes.  
- Option P01 - Premium Package, consisting of: activated ventilated (heated and cooled) seats, electronic trunk closer, Airscarf (heated headrest blower), and Keyless Go (push-button start and keyless entry) 
 
The engine is in mint condition. I never experienced any hesitation or detonation; it doesn't burn any oil or knock on startup. The motor pulls strong through the rev range. Transmission shifts rapidly every time. I have not had a single repair needed since I purchased the vehicle. I never saw any DTC records appear (check engine light).   
 
Interior is in mint condition. All electronic systems work perfectly and I know it connects with iPhone generations 4, 5 and 6.  
 
Exterior is in excellent condition -- there is one minor blemish on the front fender that was present when I bought it in March of 2014. Paint is in excellent condition -- I wax and clay block it regularly. I replaced the lower lip on front bumper due to scratches from the occasional steep driveway.  
 
The 2009 SL63 is a well-built car produced after the breakup of DaimlerChrysler (often noted for the reduced build quality of Mercedes Benz vehicles under their reign) and has no Recalls, Investigations, or Complaints according to the National Highway Transportation Administration (NHTSA: www.safercar.gov).  
 
This car, like most used vehicles sold privately, is sold as-is with no implied or expressed warranty. Buyer may have the vehicle inspected at their own cost at a reputable local mechanic.  
 
At this time, I am not interested in trades. Serious buyers only please.

Added performance items are Vance and Hines True Dual exhaust headers, with chrome heat shields. The slip on mufflers are Bub 7. Beautiful sound, not too loud. title: 1997 Honda Civic LX - smogged, registered, clean title, gasket leak
description:
Hi, I'm selling my 1997 Honda Civic LX. It starts and runs great. It has a clean title, clean carfax report, it is smogged, is currently registered, and has meticulously kept car mechanic records for its ENTIRE HISTORY. 
 
Just a few months ago, we took it to a mechanic and put several thousands dollars worth of work into this car because we were planning to drive it for the next 10 years. 
 
It has: 
 
1. New tires 
2. New radiator 
3. A new radiator overflow tank 
4. New thermostat 
5. New hoses 
6. New distributer cap and rotor 
7. New spark plugs 
8. New exhaust manifold 
9. New catalytic converter 
10. New drive axel 
11. New timing belt (<10,000 miles on it) 
12. All new drive belts 
 
The exterior is in fair shape - it has some dents and dings and peeling paint. 
 
The interior is in fair/good shape. There are some stains as you can see in the picture. 
 
Everything works - AC, cruise control, nice aftermarket stereo with iphone charger & cd player, all automated windows work with the exception of one back window. 
 
Here's the bad news: 
 
After my boyfriend had the radiator overflow replaced, there were air pockets in the radiator. After driving on the highway, the engine overheated. It was not safe to immediately pull over, so it took a couple of minutes before he turned off the car. When we took it to the mechanic's, and they diagnosed a small leak in the head gasket. The leak is currently very small and almost unnoticeable but it's there. We parked the car IMMEDIATELY (within 30 miles of it being diagnosed) with the goal of eventually rebuilding our engine.  
 
However, realistically, we're busy and could use the money for other higher priority projects. Our loss is your gain.  
 
If you're handy and interested in purchasing, email or text us. I screen my phone calls so just text me to get an answer.  
 
The price is firm. Please bring cash in hand. Serious inquiries only please. 
 
Thanks in advance, 
-Tara

title: Pair of (2 x) Xeon X5679 Westmere Hex Core 3.2Ghz 6.4GT/s 115w TDP
description:
Hello, 
 
I have for sale a pair (2 CPUs) of new Intel Xeon Hex Core X5679 CPUs. 
 
These are 6 core CPUs, 2 CPUs = 12 cores with 24 threads. 
 
They were purchased from a major Enterprise IT reseller (Intel/Dell/HP partner), and never used. I opened sealed packages only to take pictures. 
 
I believe they most likely pulled them from a new HP or Dell workstation or server. 
 
If you buy these CPUs, I will throw in 24GB of free PC3-16000R ECC memory as a bonus. 
 
At one point, these CPUs set a world speed record (overclocked), and were ranked higher in the Passmark CPU Benchmark than Xeon X5680, and roughly equal to X5690 CPUs: 
 
http://www.cpubenchmark.net/cpu.php?cpu=Intel+Xeon+X5679+%40+3.20GHz&id=1311&cpuCount=2 
 
http://cpuboss.com/cpus/Intel-Xeon-X5690-vs-Intel-Xeon-5600-X5679 
 
They are lower voltage 115 watts maximum consumed power and therefore run cooler and more efficiently compared to X5680 and X5690. This means they can overclock to very fast speeds (4.6Ghz, and probably faster with liquid or gas cooling). 
 
http://www.cpu-world.com/CPUs/Xeon/Intel-Xeon%20X5679%20-%20AT80614006924AA.html

title: Roland Jupiter-80 Synthesizer, like new, in custom road case on wheels
description:
THE best synth for performing musician ever produced, period, top choice of A-list acts. 256-note polyphony, layering, effects, arpeggiator. Zillion of ready-made sounds from Roland's acclaimed SuperNatural library, including recreation of signature patches from legends of the past -- Jupiter-6 and -8, Juno-60 and -106, JX-series, D-50, SH-101, TB-303 and many others. Every sound you can possibly think of is here, built-in, instantly accessible. No need to dig deep in menu layers, browse through banks and cards, everything is right on the surface! 
 
Jupiter-80 is extremely powerful synth, more than anything else on the market, but also very user-friendly, unlike Korg Kronos, Nord and many others. Quick access buttons let you recall favorite sounds quickly, while touch screen makes editing a breeze. Everything is designed with live performers in mind, with quick and easy access. You can layer and split over keyboard no less than 10 (ten!) parts (individual sounds). This way you can play, for example bassline and pads, or pads and solos, or create unique layered combinations. Possibilities are really endless, limited only by your imagination! 
 
One unique feature of JP-80 is registration buttons. Located right below the keyboard, it lets you store and instantly recall 256 performance memories (any combination of sounds), by pressing two buttons at most! A life-saver during live performance, when every second counts: you press those with your thumb, no need to even take hands off the keyboard! No other synth on the market has these! 
 
Another handy feature is USB player/recorder. You can record your performance as 2-track stereo, or, if you are using backing tracks, play them straight from USB, with separate level and 4-band EQ controls. Similar to a digital mixer, except all this is done inside JP-80, nothing else is needed. Recording can be done in any format, up to .WAV at 96K, so you can import your performance straight into any DAW, Pro Tools, Logic, whatever, like it was a soft synth. It also has stereo line input at the back, handy for playing backing track or break music straight from iPhone. Also convenient when learning covers: you can hear the original and play along, no other equipment is needed. 
 
Too many features to even list here. Read more online and watch videos on YouTube, there are plenty. Here are some: 
Full features demo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=afS_wDWDnbU 
Jonathan Cain (JOURNEY) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2JlMv3F7zLc 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eyKf1Ixublg 
Synth legends demo: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HRkSST5032g 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=229Stlmb86I 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=92gkfGRTafU 
 
Synth is in new condition, not even a single scratch anywhere. Works flawlessly, 100%. Firmware was updated to the most recent v.2.11, with all "Classic Collection" sounds from the legends of the past: Jupiter-8, Juno-106, JP-8000, and even some brass, piano and bass sounds from another classic: Yamaha DX-7! Was stored in custom-ordered road case from day one, used in studio only, never taken out on the road. The case alone is worth at least $400, also brand new. Also included is a custom soft cover by DigitalDeskCovers. 
 
Located in San Mateo, you can come and test it any way you want. Available most days until 7pm. 
 
Since you see this ad now, it means that synth is STILL AVAILABLE.

title: BRAND NEW Axon 7 ZTE Cell Phone
description:
I have a brand new, never used, still in box 64gb unlocked Axon 7 ZTE smart phone.  The only reason I'm selling is because I bought 2 phones from Best Buy and ended up going with the other brand because it was a tiny bit smaller (this is one is about the same size as the iPhone 6).  I am showing photos of the exact model that I bought with its features, along with the one I have to show that it's in mint condition and still with its box. I did a ton of research when I went to buy a new phone and this smart phone is listed right up there with iPhones and Samsung but at a much more reasonable price.  Great buy for someone not wanting to spend $800 on a new phone! 
 
Product Features 
 
Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 processor 
Quad-core 2.15GHz processor and 4GB of RAM deliver outstanding overall performance for opening and running applications, flipping through menus, running home screens and more. 
Android 6.0.1 Marshmallow OS 
Offers a fresh, fast platform to help you stay connected and productive while you're on the go. 
Compatible GSM carriers, including AT&T and T-Mobile 
Also compatible with prepaid SIM Kits, including Net10, H2O, GoPhone and Simple Wireless. 
4G LTE speed 
Provides fast Web connection for downloading apps, streaming content and staying connected with social media. 
5.5" AMOLED touch screen 
Extra-large screen is matched with a slim body to comfortably fit in your hand. Offers 16:9 cinema-like screen ratio that's perfect for viewing of videos, photos and games. 
20MP rear-facing camera for 1080p Full HD video recording 
Dedicated light sensor enables the camera to capture more light in dark environments for better pictures. Also includes a front-facing 8MP camera for self-portraits and video. 
64GB internal memory plus microSD slot 
Extensive storage space for your contacts, music, photos, apps and more. Expand storage up to 128GB by adding a microSD card (sold separately). 
Dual SIM Card Design 
Two SIM card slots allow you to combine two numbers and networks on the same phone. Great for traveling abroad, separating personal and business contacts, or switching to a stronger network based on your location. 
Use your smartphone as a mobile hotspot 
Share your 4G data connection with other compatible wireless devices.* 
Your fingerprint keeps your phone secure 
Swipe your finger on the backside sensor panel to unlock your phone. 
Access to Google Play 
Browse and download apps, magazines, books, movies, and television programs directly to your phone. 
Listen to your favorite tunes 
Store and play your MP3 files on your phone. 
*SIM card not included. 
 
Retails for $400 new, I'm selling at $375. Price is firm. Serious inquiries only please. Thanks!

With each purchase over $100.00 (before taxes), you will receive any antique Christmas present you chose from under our Christmas tree that is wrapped in green paper. Each gift is something I randomly pick from our antique shop to wrap and put under our tree. The gift's value is about 1/4+ of the required purchase amount. These are not antiques or extravagant gifts but just something to say thank you for your business and may you have a Very Merry Christmas. The Christmas season is our most favorite time of the year. Just come and take a look around our 9 room shop and see if we can get you into the Christmas spirit while sipping on complementary hot cider, wassail, coffee, tea or cocoa. Our shop consists of 3 rooms full of primitive/rustic antiques, 1 room with higher end antiques, 2 rooms with more common antiques and 3 rooms stocked with flea market/garage sale type items. We are also selling cranberries at $2.00 per pound. In our Cranberry Room, we recently set up our full antique legendary Hayden sorting line which consist of our blower, elevator, separator and front sorting trays. Watch as our cranberries are sorted the same way as they were over 100 years ago. Our antique shop is located in a former cranberry screen house which was called "The New England Cranberry Sales Company" (built in 1918) where the same process took place over 90 years. Before visiting us, we strongly suggest that you call, text or email us ahead of time to avoid disappointment just in case something comes up and we cannot be here to greet you. Hours: Monday - Friday 12 noon - 6 PM Saturday 10 AM - 4 PM Sunday 12 noon - 4 PM We except all major credit cards and cash of course. But no checks of any type -- sorry. Hayden Separator Antique Shop Hayden Mfg. Co. Inc. 70 Carver Rd. W. Wareham MA We are proudly celebrating 124 years in our family business supplying the cranberry industry with goods and services. We are looking forward meeting you and sharing the history of our family business with you. A very merry Christmas and a Happy New Year to all of you!
